@startuml NeuroGraph-CodeRAG System Context

!theme plain
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam padding 15
skinparam arrowThickness 2

title System Context Diagram - NeuroGraph-CodeRAG

' External Actors
actor "Developer" as Dev #LightBlue
database "Code\nRepository" as Repo #LightGray
database "Training\nDatasets" as Data #LightGray

' System Boundary
rectangle "NeuroGraph-CodeRAG System" #E8F5E9 {
    component "Code Summarization\nEngine" as System #4CAF50
}

' External Dependencies
cloud "Gemma-2b\nLLM" as LLM #FFE0B2
cloud "CodeBERT\nEmbeddings" as CodeBERT #E1BEE7

' Relationships
Dev --> System : "Submit code\nfor summarization"
System --> Dev : "Return natural\nlanguage summary"

Repo --> System : "Provide source code\nand dependencies"
Data --> System : "Training examples"

System --> LLM : "Generate summaries\n(with LoRA)"
System --> CodeBERT : "Encode code\nfor retrieval"

note right of System
  **Core Capabilities:**
  • Multi-view structural analysis
    (AST, CFG, PDG, Call Graph)
  • RAG-enhanced context
  • Agentic self-correction
  • Repository-wide understanding
end note

@enduml
